BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20150129T203914Z
UID:b053e218-fbbe-4054-a484-60419165c423
SUMMARY:Mobilising the small business economy
DESCRIPTION:Small businesses drive the UK economy\, but what drives small b
 usinesses? Karren will be talking about the future for UK small businesses
  and how cloud technology enabled firms play a pivotal role in supporting 
 enterprising business owners\, and helping the UK economy reach its potent
 ial in 2015 and beyond.
DTSTART:20150210T091500Z
DTEND:20150210T101500Z
END:VEVENT
