UID:1ba19e4d-6924-4c38-abc5-ce523b74c8d9
SUMMARY:The connected business platform
DESCRIPTION:Rod will take you through what’s coming next in the journey t
 o a truly connected cloud business platform. He’ll explore the opportuni
 ties emerging for innovative Accounting Practices and how we can all succe
 ed if we work together.
DTSTART:20150210T104500Z
DTEND:20150210T113000Z
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20150129T203914Z
UID:f7497d29-aa89-481c-9eb3-c1802f4e1b1b
SUMMARY:Empowering small business for growth
DESCRIPTION:Together with Xero you’ve already built the foundations of th
 e UK cloud accounting industry. What comes next is going to be even more e
 xciting as we take the opportunity to build on these foundations\, mobilis
 e small businesses and drive economic growth. Gary will give an update of 
 Xero in the UK and you’ll learn how as the founders of the UK cloud acco
 unting industry you have a unique opportunity to lead industry change and 
 economic progress.
DTSTART:20150210T113000Z
DTEND:20150210T121500Z
END:VEVENT
