UID:4a797181-93ed-497a-864d-b7a5ec43437c
SUMMARY:The future of business and technology
DESCRIPTION:David will be talking about the big technology picture for cons
 umers and businesses\, and will explain how you can prepare yourself and y
 our business to thrive and grow as these new trends take shape.
DTSTART:20150210T133000Z
DTEND:20150210T143000Z
