SUMMARY:Embrace change and achieve greatness
DESCRIPTION:Change. Where do you start? You’ve seen the future\, how do y
 ou get there? Andy will be talking about managing change and how to become
  the practice of the future. Hear how Andy’s experiences in Silicon Vall
 ey and the international banking industry directly translate into actionab
 le learnings that will change your outlook and the way you run your practi
 ce.
DTSTART:20150210T143000Z
DTEND:20150210T151500Z
